{"tid":991301,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"《訴苦》仲有幾多個朋友keep到 ?","createTime":"2019-01-22T09:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:39:11.000Z","uid":232359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53a5688c10b1a3724c7c54e21052657bb764aa52","tid":991301,"uid":232359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"好懷念以前讀書果陣同《好朋友》小息9沖去買撈麵，放學三五成群結隊去球場打波或者打機，果陣真係好快樂，有咩心事會互相分享，有野我會第一個知。<br />\n<br />\n但宜家慢慢一個比一個疏遠，次次約親打機食飯人數一次比一次少。心事慢慢都唔會同我再分享，變得收收埋埋。唔知係米升上大學，有左屬於自己圈子，忘記左以前友誼。<br />\n<br />\n唉，同埋我明白到年紀慢慢大都要踏入社會，工作，拍拖，有屬於自己世界，但希望曾經《好朋友》可以記得中學果份友誼。"},{"pid":"7f013d1a0f3b621b7345c99fb0647d00bb14a0dc","tid":991301,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a7a0ad5741c4ee1aef34ba78c5243f85653756","tid":991301,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:38:35.000Z","msg":"時間唔夠分配姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d174b43474afd2dad2fd32676ddb33cd96b89f","tid":991301,"uid":177115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"今年year2，但係都可以同中學班好兄弟每星期食飯去玩覺得好好、好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19930e4862ae617812243c5c4a00cacfb4629d36","tid":991301,"uid":232359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d174b43474afd2dad2fd32676ddb33cd96b89f","tid":991301,"uid":177115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"今年year2，但係都可以同中學班好兄弟每星期食飯去玩覺得好好、好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"一開始都有吖， 慢慢會因為反工同學習而唔夠時間見面"}]}